text: Metachroma orientale is a species of leaf beetle. It is found in coastal states in the United States, ranging from Texas to Florida to Massachusetts. Its length is between 3.5 and 4.7 mm. ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * * Category:Eumolpinae Category:Taxa named by Doris Holmes Blake Category:Beetles described in 1970
title: Metachroma orientale
